[
	{
		"id": 0,
		"localized_name": "カロリン",
		"romanized_name": "Caroline",
		"model_path_hash": "5485149628928083359",
		"text": "ハイディ。あなたのお母様が私を雇われた理由は、\n先ほど申し上げた通りです",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5434631736340677129",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 1,
		"localized_name": "カロリン",
		"romanized_name": "Caroline",
		"model_path_hash": "5485149628928083359",
		"text": "お父様から申し込まれた決闘……\nその、代理の出席者を立てるため",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5434631736340677129",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 2,
		"localized_name": "ハイディ",
		"romanized_name": "Heidi",
		"model_path_hash": "5270784299656074783",
		"text": "まさか、ご両親サマがここまで険悪な仲だとは",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "120518867847693403",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 3,
		"localized_name": "ハイディ",
		"romanized_name": "Heidi",
		"model_path_hash": "5270784299656074783",
		"text": "あの二人、昔からケンカばっかりだったんだ。\n私がやめてって言っても、やめてくれなかった",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "120518867847693403",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 4,
		"localized_name": "ハイディ",
		"romanized_name": "Heidi",
		"model_path_hash": "5270784299656074783",
		"text": "家出したのも、それが嫌だったからなんだよね。\n毎日うるさいし。家の中、ピリピリしてるし",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "120518867847693403",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 5,
		"localized_name": "ハイディ",
		"romanized_name": "Heidi",
		"model_path_hash": "5270784299656074783",
		"text": "……それがまさか、決闘だとかいう\n馬鹿げた話にまで拗れるなんて",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "120518867847693403",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 6,
		"localized_name": "カロリン",
		"romanized_name": "Caroline",
		"model_path_hash": "5485149628928083359",
		"text": "ケンカの原因はなんなのでしょう？",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5434631736340677129",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 7,
		"localized_name": "ハイディ",
		"romanized_name": "Heidi",
		"model_path_hash": "5270784299656074783",
		"text": "たぶん、仕事上の考え方の違いからくるものだよ",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "120518867847693403",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 8,
		"localized_name": "カロリン",
		"romanized_name": "Caroline",
		"model_path_hash": "5485149628928083359",
		"text": "ご両親とも考古学者でしたね。同じ道を歩んでいる\nからこそ、折り合わないところがあるのでしょう",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5434631736340677129",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 9,
		"localized_name": "ハイディ",
		"romanized_name": "Heidi",
		"model_path_hash": "5270784299656074783",
		"text": "……私が家からいなくなっても、\n変わらなかったんだね。何も",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "120518867847693403",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 10,
		"localized_name": "カロリン",
		"romanized_name": "Caroline",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "…………",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5434631736340677129",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 11,
		"localized_name": "カロリン",
		"romanized_name": "Caroline",
		"model_path_hash": "5485149628928083359",
		"text": "それでもあなたは、仲間と旅を共にするのではなく、\nここに来ることを選ばれました",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5434631736340677129",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 12,
		"localized_name": "カロリン",
		"romanized_name": "Caroline",
		"model_path_hash": "5485149628928083359",
		"text": "よかったのですか？",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5434631736340677129",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 13,
		"localized_name": "ハイディ",
		"romanized_name": "Heidi",
		"model_path_hash": "5270784299656074783",
		"text": "……迷ったけど、さ",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "120518867847693403",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 14,
		"localized_name": "ハイディ",
		"romanized_name": "Heidi",
		"model_path_hash": "5270784299656074783",
		"text": "ヴァレリアやフロッケ、そしてランツェと過ごして、\n家族のぬくもりってやつを知っちゃったからさ",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "120518867847693403",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 15,
		"localized_name": "ハイディ",
		"romanized_name": "Heidi",
		"model_path_hash": "5270784299656074783",
		"text": "やっぱり家族は仲良くないと、後味が悪い",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "120518867847693403",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 16,
		"localized_name": "ハイディ",
		"romanized_name": "Heidi",
		"model_path_hash": "5270784299656074783",
		"text": "昔は逃げてばっかりだったけど、今は違う。\n家族の問題にはちゃんと向き合うことにしたんだ",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "120518867847693403",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 17,
		"localized_name": "カロリン",
		"romanized_name": "Caroline",
		"model_path_hash": "5485149628928083359",
		"text": "……本当に頼もしくなられましたね",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5434631736340677129",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 18,
		"localized_name": "カロリン",
		"romanized_name": "Caroline",
		"model_path_hash": "5485149628928083359",
		"text": "今のハイディなら、\nきっとご両親とも向き合えるはずです",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5434631736340677129",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 19,
		"localized_name": "ハイディ",
		"romanized_name": "Heidi",
		"model_path_hash": "5270784299656074783",
		"text": "ありがと、カロリン。\nあんたがそう言ってくれると心強いよ",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "120518867847693403",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 20,
		"localized_name": "カロリン",
		"romanized_name": "Caroline",
		"model_path_hash": "5485149628928083359",
		"text": "私もできる限りお力添えいたします。\nさあ、ご実家へ参りましょう",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5434631736340677129",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 21,
		"localized_name": "ハイディ",
		"romanized_name": "Heidi",
		"model_path_hash": "5270784299656074783",
		"text": "ああ。全部片付けて、胸張って新天地へ行くんだ。\n……さ、行こう！",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "120518867847693403",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	}
]